      "modality": "text",
      "content": "Set coordinates A(0,0,0), B(2,0,0), D(1,sqrt(3),0), C(3,sqrt(3),0), and P(0,0,1) from AB=AD=2, angle BAD=60 degrees, and PA perpendicular to the base plane.",
